name: Lucy Enigma Series 001: Sarche
description:
Lucy Enigma Series 001: Sarche

love flower, be garden is an affirmation music by Lucy enigma - Sarche, 
Sarche is a thank for humans, and living things 

This materialistic world makes it difficult to do something without considering the surrounding; 
humans should be able to humanize, be grounded, and spread love; 
all species should be able to do whatever they want to do 
what is best for themselves and provide love to others.

Flowers mean Self
Garden means kindness and positive energy
